# Resize

# Take Snapshot and Resize together!
https://fabianlee.org/2020/02/23/kvm-testing-cloud-init-locally-using-kvm-for-an-ubuntu-cloud-image/

`# original image is 2G, create snapshot and make it 30G
qemu-img create -b $origin.img -f qcow2 snapshot.qcow2 30G`



